        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="75.609" end="x">Hm. What was your father's occupation?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="82.038" end="x"> A field-worker [farm worker].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="83.577" end="x">A field...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="84.392" end="x"> Earth-worker.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="85.418" end="x">What was he? What did he do?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="87.471" end="x"> In the fields...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="89.855" end="x">Did he own his fields?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="91.062" end="x"> His own...he worked on his own fields.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="92.330" end="x">He was a 'farmer'?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="93.869" end="x"> Yes, he was.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="94.684" end="x">And what did he plant?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="96.706" end="x"> Trees, wheat...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="99.970" end="x">Wheat. Yes?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="101.298" end="x"> ...wheat and food stuffs...bread...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
