                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="121.363" end="x">But...</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="122.027" end="x"> ...when we were taken away to camp...<a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>...and that is when they perished.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="126.343" end="x">You weren't allowed to liquidate your...to sell your belongings, or so?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Samuel Isakovitch</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#isakovitchS" start="132.047" end="x"> No, no. Everything remained. We were taken away from the house and everything was taken away. Everything remained there with the house.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="140.083" end="x">Hm. Now let us start from the beginning. When did the Germans come to your town?</span>
        </li>
                <li>
